info.name: StackOverflow Bathys with Chat Fixes [WIP]
info.description: This style combines the dark colored theme style 87150 & style 90325 with some adjusted colors as chat rooms were having trouble with default colour scheme.
info.additionalInfo:
- Fixed stars in chat window
- constrained styles to stay in chat (the leak from chat side was looking horrible on SO)
- Fixed rooms joined color
- Made the gold badge color a tad darker as it was really hard on eyes on a dark background. Also adjusted shadow (1px nudge) to help the white text.
- Added colors to textarea, input and .question-status that was appearing grey on grey.
- Shaded the chat's bottom panel to match rest of the theme.
- Fixed more shades on main chat rooms page & chat room information page
